main event: A report of a UFO sighting that involved an object with blinking lights traveling from left to right across the sky.
interesting points: The sighting occurred over the Atlantic Ocean at a latitude of 60°37N and longitude of 11°02W.,The object was seen for 4 minutes and was observed at an altitude of approximately 300 degrees.,The object was described as having a satellite character, possibly being an Echo.,The sighting was recorded at midnight on January 20, 1963.,It was lost in evening twilight after traveling a distance of about 1/2 mile.
